name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Rachelle Road - 2016
description:
I have just rediscovered a 2016 Processing language project I did which explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. I have decided to resurrect it as a series of "video postcards". This is a taster... mp4, 1152x824px, 35seconds(please loop), 58.8MB.

It means I will need to update my version of Processing and rewrite the code, but that should be a bit of a fun break amidst my other projects (see https://aliasrubytuesday.art). Once rewritten I'll randomly drop new postcards... hope you like them.
